    "name": "geneWeave A2A Protocol",
    "description": "A2A JSON-RPC 2.0 tests for geneWeave.\n\nFlow:\n1. Run Auth > Login first — the test script saves the Bearer token automatically.\n2. Run any A2A request.\n\nCredentials (local dev):\n  email:    a2a-postman@weaveintel.test\n  password: Postman1!\n\nFor CSV requests set the collection variable csvBase64:\n  macOS:  base64 -i examples/data/sales.csv | tr -d '\\n'\n  Linux:  base64 -w 0 examples/data/sales.csv",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
